title: Cruz'n Hawaii Part 1
description: The Santa Cruz team visits beautiful Hawaii. In Part 1, the crew handles some heavy Hawaiian transitions, visits Cholo's bowl and rock jump into the pacific blue. Featuring Shuriken, Strubing, Salba, Dressen, Eman, Sid and even Mr. Hand tagged along.
